%F A061278 a(n+1) = Sum_{k=0..n} U(k, 2) = Sum_{k=0..n} S(k, 4), where U(n,x) and S(n,x) are Chebyshev polynomials. - _Paul Barry_, Nov 14 2003
%F A061278 G.f.: x/(1 - 5*x + 5*x^2 - x^3).
